  <div class="col-md-10">
    <p>We identified a common use for our Rewards program that was repetitive, time consuming, &amp; too easily administered incorrectly: rewarding workers for their long service!</p>
    <p>We wanted to act quickly and turn around a bespoke experience for these organizations.</p>
    <p class="mt-4"><strong>The Bet</strong><br />Build a component that tracks worker hire dates and organizes them in to an easily digestible anniversary list. Help admins never miss the opportunity to recognize service with an item from the Workhub Rewards catalog. Additionally, provide comprehensive tools to build a strong yearly program that reflects the values of an organization.</p>
    <p>We can utilize Workhub's ability to provide quiality embroidered soft goods and leverage that against the favourable Canadian tax code for anniversary gifts.</p>
