      <p>With interest confirmed, we started mapping out the user personas and what their primary flows were going to require:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>The Setup Admin</strong> needs it to be a easy as possible to start recognizing years of service at their organization</li>
        <li><strong>The Manager</strong> needs to be able to track, approve redemptions, and update the program over time</li>
        <li><strong>The Worker</strong> needs to be notified of an anniversary, easily select an exciting item, and have it shippied to their address of choice</li>
      </ul>
      <p>It was an immense help that most of this functionality was to be built on the foundation of Rewards. <a href="https://www.workhub.com/features/branded-apparel/" target="_blank">Read more about Workhub Rewards here</a></p>
